<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>noel House 🥇</title>
  {% set css %}
    {% include "style.css" %}
  {% endset %}
  <style>
    {{ css | cssmin | safe }}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="contents">
    <header>
      <h1>trello-connecting</h1>
      <p>
        <a href="{{ site.trello_board }}">트렐로 보드</a>에 연결되어 <a href="https://netlify.com{{ site.utm }}">Netlify</a>에 자동으로 배포 됩니다.
      </p>
    </header>
  </div>
  <main>
    {% for card in trello %}
    <section>
      <h2>{{ card.name }}</h2>
      <div>
      {% markdown %}
        {{- card.desc | safe }}
      {% endmarkdown %}
      </div>
    </section>
    {% endfor %}
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>티스토리 : <a href="{{ site.tistory }}">tistory</a></p>
    <p>깃허브 : <a href="{{ site.github }}">github</a></p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
